* if their bonds went back up.


  [2] Also, I mean, here we are in a debt-ceiling crisis; Treasury is not a=
bout to pay 100 for bonds worth 85 when every penny counts. Though when I s=
ay =E2=80=9Cthe government=E2=80=9D I *mostly*, though not entirely, mean t=
